task.summary: Moved mLine.setPoints() outside the while loop in reinstateMap() in RunMapFragment.java
Initial creation of PointsHolder and BoundsHolder for passing LatLng List and LatLngBounds into RunMapFragment.
Folded BoundsHolder and PointsHolder into RunManager; elimiinated redundant code in RunMapFragment.
Created AsyncTask to initialize LatLngBounds and List<LatLng> in RunFragment for use by RunMapFragment; other minor cleanup in RunFragment.
Miscellaneous cleanup of code and comments following Android Studio inspection of project.

Further clean up and consolidation of code in RunMapFragment, consolidation of sort and adapter configuration portions of RunPagerActivity, and fix for inability to delete last Run from RunPagerActivity following deletion of other Runs.
Minor clean up of code identifying RunId after deletion of Run and related comments
Minor changes to comments in RunPagerActivity.java
Fixed minor initial layout problem in RunMapFragment.
Changes to code for updating, recording and displaying starting and ending addresses in RunFragment
Changed method for calculating duration back to summing time differences of location updates from difference between last location time and start location time.
